## 9. Definition of Done

`P12` complete when ALL are true:

* [ ] Extension manifest parsed and converted to `ExtensionManifest` type
* [ ] Sandbox executor working with vm + worker_threads
* [ ] API bridge proxying through permission gate
* [ ] Agent tool injection working (installed extension visible in agent tool list)
* [ ] Skill runner successfully executes 3-step skill
* [ ] `design-tokens.ts` exists, all tokens sourced from it
* [ ] 60+ components migrated, no gray/stone conflict
* [ ] Dark mode consistent across all components
* [ ] Table font minimum 12px
* [ ] No mobile toolbar overflow, sidebar works
* [ ] All unit tests passing
* [ ] Visual regression tests passing

---

## 10. Rollback Playbook

**Trigger conditions:**
* Sandbox escape detected (security)
* Agent tool injection breaks existing plan execution
* Design migration produces visual regression

**Rollback procedure:**
1. Set `extensionRuntime.enabled: false` flag — extensions disabled, existing executor unaffected
2. For design migration: each component is an independent commit, revert single file
3. If `design-tokens.ts` change is reverted: components revert to old inline strings (automated codemod reversed)

---

## 11. What Next Phase Inherits

`P13` inherits:
* Working extension runtime host
* Permission-gated API bridge
* Skill runner infrastructure
* Clean design token system
* Mobile-ready dashboard

`P13` may add:
* Orchestrator daemon (P11.B — most critical gap)
* Self-improvement loop (P11.H)
* Organic memory pipeline

